##
# Steam Flatpak bind mount
#
# The flatpak for protonup-qt expects this Steam/data directory to exist, but sometimes will fail
# to symlink it if the symlink already exists. We can avoid this problem by mounting the directory
# as a bind mount.
~/.var/app/com.valvesoftware.Steam/.local/share ~/.var/app/com.valvesoftware.Steam/data   none    defaults,bind,nofail    0 0
